  "description": "A close-up, low-angle shot focuses on the delicate petals of a tulip. The flower is predominantly a deep, rich crimson with subtle gradations of darker shades near the edges. A gentle transition to a warm, golden yellow is visible where the petal curves inward, creating a visually appealing contrast. The stem, a vibrant green, is partially visible, offering a stark contrast against the dark background. The lighting is dramatic, highlighting the petal's texture and form, and creating a soft, blurred effect in the background. The image emphasizes the organic curves and natural beauty of the flower.",
